{"word":"ἀγνωμονέω","slug":"ἀγνωμονέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀγνωμονέω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀγνώμων'><el>ἀγνώμων</el></a>\n<p/><i>to act without right feeling, act unfairly</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>; <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be unfairly treated</i>, <el>ἀγνωμονηθείς</el> <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/>"}]}